{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1028,"text":"I love to collect things."},{"time":3187,"text":"Ever since I was a kid, I've had massive collections"},{"time":5177,"text":"of random stuff, everything from bizarre hot sauces"},{"time":7906,"text":"from all around the world to insects"},{"time":11144,"text":"that I've captured and put in jars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13548,"text":"Now, it's no secret, because I like collecting things,"},{"time":15585,"text":"that I love the Natural History Museum"},{"time":17521,"text":"and the collections of animals"},{"time":18921,"text":"at the Natural History Museum in dioramas."},{"time":20736,"text":"These, to me, are like living sculptures, right,"},{"time":22873,"text":"that you can go and look at,"},{"time":24290,"text":"and they memorialize a specific point of time"},{"time":26025,"text":"in this animal's life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27672,"text":"So I was thinking about my own life,"},{"time":29554,"text":"and how I'd like to memorialize my life, you know,"},{"time":31467,"text":"for the ages, and also — (Laughter) —"},{"time":34250,"text":"the lives of my friends, but"},{"time":36737,"text":"the problem with this is that my friends aren't quite keen"},{"time":39353,"text":"on the idea of me taxidermy-ing them. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":42529,"text":"So instead, I turned to video,"},{"time":45232,"text":"and video is the next best way to preserve and memorialize"},{"time":47530,"text":"someone and to capture a specific moment in time."},{"time":50304,"text":"So what I did was, I filmed six of my friends"},{"time":52481,"text":"and then, using video mapping and video projection,"},{"time":54881,"text":"I created a video sculpture, which was these six friends"},{"time":57362,"text":"projected into jars. (Laughter)"},{"time":61304,"text":"So now I have this collection of my friends"},{"time":63018,"text":"I can take around with me whenever I go,"},{"time":64807,"text":"and this is called Animalia Chordata,"},{"time":66719,"text":"from the Latin nomenclature for"},{"time":68536,"text":"human being, classification system."},{"time":70696,"text":"So this piece memorializes my friends in these jars,"},{"time":73658,"text":"and they actually move around. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78017,"text":"So, this is interesting to me,"},{"time":80110,"text":"but it lacked a certain human element. (Laughter)"},{"time":84000,"text":"It's a digital sculpture, so I wanted to add"},{"time":85822,"text":"an interaction system. So what I did was,"},{"time":87434,"text":"I added a proximity sensor, so that when you get close"},{"time":89217,"text":"to the people in jars, they react to you in different ways."},{"time":91376,"text":"You know, just like people on the street"},{"time":93103,"text":"when you get too close to them."},{"time":94959,"text":"Some people reacted in terror. (Laughter)"},{"time":97545,"text":"Others reacted in asking you for help,"},{"time":99558,"text":"and some people hide from you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103056,"text":"So this was really interesting to me, this idea of"},{"time":104687,"text":"taking video off the screen and putting it in real life,"},{"time":106822,"text":"and also adding interactivity to sculpture."},{"time":109069,"text":"So over the next year, I documented 40 of my other friends"},{"time":113134,"text":"and trapped them in jars as well"},{"time":114966,"text":"and created a piece known as Garden,"},{"time":116911,"text":"which is literally a garden of humanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119263,"text":"But something about the first piece,"},{"time":121407,"text":"the Animali Chordata piece, kept coming back to me,"},{"time":123312,"text":"this idea of interaction with art,"},{"time":125133,"text":"and I really liked the idea of people being able to interact,"},{"time":127455,"text":"and also being challenged by interacting with art."},{"time":129744,"text":"So I wanted to create a new piece that actually"},{"time":131599,"text":"forced people to come and interact with something,"},{"time":133488,"text":"and the way I did this was actually by projecting"},{"time":135187,"text":"a 1950s housewife into a blender. (Laughter)"},{"time":139567,"text":"This is a piece called Blend, and what it does is"},{"time":142062,"text":"it actually makes you implicit in the work of art."},{"time":143925,"text":"You may never experience the entire thing yourself."},{"time":146266,"text":"You can walk away, you can just watch as this character"},{"time":148590,"text":"stands there in the blender and looks at you,"},{"time":151015,"text":"or you can actually choose to interact with it."},{"time":153089,"text":"So if you do choose to interact with the piece,"},{"time":157222,"text":"and you press the blender button, it actually sends"},{"time":159382,"text":"this character into this dizzying disarray of dishevelment."},{"time":162814,"text":"By doing that, you are now part of my piece."},{"time":166366,"text":"You, like the people that are trapped in my work"},{"time":168398,"text":"— (Blender noises, laughter) —"},{"time":172459,"text":"have become part of my work as well. (Laughter)"},{"time":179566,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":181759,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":184182,"text":"But, but this seems a bit unfair, right?"},{"time":187822,"text":"I put my friends in jars, I put this character,"},{"time":190334,"text":"this sort of endangered species character in a blender."},{"time":193151,"text":"But I'd never done anything about myself."},{"time":195151,"text":"I'd never really memorialized myself."},{"time":196863,"text":"So I decided to create a piece which is a self-portrait piece."},{"time":199133,"text":"This is sort of a self-portrait taxidermy time capsule piece"},{"time":201358,"text":"called A Point Just Passed,"},{"time":203605,"text":"in which I project myself on top of a time card punch clock,"},{"time":206237,"text":"and it's up to you."},{"time":207941,"text":"If you want to choose to punch that punch card clock,"},{"time":209887,"text":"you actually age me."},{"time":211594,"text":"So I start as a baby, and then if you punch the clock,"},{"time":214150,"text":"you'll actually transform the baby into a toddler,"},{"time":218812,"text":"and then from a toddler I'm transformed into a teenager."},{"time":222043,"text":"From a teenager, I'm transformed into my current self."},{"time":224563,"text":"From my current self, I'm turned into a middle-aged man,"},{"time":227651,"text":"and then, from there, into an elderly man."},{"time":231510,"text":"And if you punch the punch card clock a hundred times"},{"time":234442,"text":"in one day, the piece goes black"},{"time":237513,"text":"and is not to be reset until the next day."},{"time":240206,"text":"So, in doing so, you're erasing time."},{"time":242290,"text":"You're actually implicit in this work"},{"time":244218,"text":"and you're erasing my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246224,"text":"So I like this about interactive video sculpture,"},{"time":248370,"text":"that you can actually interact with it,"},{"time":249947,"text":"that all of you can actually touch an artwork"},{"time":251819,"text":"and be part of the artwork yourselves,"},{"time":253683,"text":"and hopefully, one day, I'll have each and every one of you"},{"time":256154,"text":"trapped in one of my jars. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":258314,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}